  "title": "151.4",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "blockquote",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "As you observe the spirit, you note that he moves with a certain practiced repetition, as if he is deeply familiar with his current path. At a turn in the passage, the spirit pauses, and finally acknowledges your presence."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "He speaks to you in a startlingly deep voice, gesturing with his hands as he does. The language is that of the ancients, and while you are unable to understand it, you can still make out many familiar sounds. That, however, is where the similarites to your language end."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Despite this, you get the strong sense from his tone that he desires to be free. Perhaps he has been doomed to walk the same path for centuries, revisiting a past he would just as soon forget. If you can help this spirit break free from his familiar patterns, he might be able to move on."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "h4",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Rangers Choose"
        },
        {
          "type": "a",
          "items": [],
          "link": {
            "id": null,
            "anchor": "rangers-choose",
            "url": "#rangers-choose"
          }
        }
